abstract.description:
The configuration file used in data taking and HLT data processing step in 2010.

Run number after 150844 (appr.), software version CMSSW_3_9_1_onlpatch2 (or similar).

note.description: This file describes the exact setup for the CMS software executable which was used in a data-processing step. It is provided only for information purposes. Although all the components required to analyse the public primary datasets - such as corresponding input data, condition data, software version - are provided on this portal, it is not necessarily possible to reproduce all the described data-processing steps.
